Class KillStrategy<TMsg>

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.strategy.KillStrategy<TMsg>
  • Type Parameters:
    TMsg - The type of message that the supplied IDispatcher can send.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    IUpdateStrategy<TMsg>
    public class KillStrategy<TMsg>
extends java.lang.Object
implements IUpdateStrategy<TMsg>
    Deletes other when it collides. NOTE: This strategy only installs a "post-collision interaction behavior" and thus at least needs to be combined with a strategy that detects an interaction, e.g. Overlap or Collide.
    Author:
    Peter Dulworth (psd2), Rocky Wu (lw31)
